\begin{equation}
  \Box\bar{h}_{\mu\nu} \;=\; -\frac{16\pi G}{c^4}\,T_{\mu\nu},
  \label{eq:GW}
\end{equation}
where $\bar{h}_{\mu\nu} = h_{\mu\nu} - \frac{1}{2}\eta_{\mu\nu}h$ is the
trace-reversed perturbation.  Solutions propagate at $c$ and carry energy
