  \item Gravitational wave = traveling perturbation of the gravitational
    SSV field ($|\SSV|_{\rm abs}$ and $\mathbf{\SSV}_{\rm net}$ jointly
    perturbed in the transverse-traceless gauge).
\end{itemize}

The LIGO/Virgo/KAGRA observations of gravitational waves from binary black
